rulesfile.name: Rules for Sybase 12.5 Server-Library Migrations
rulesfile.description: Search rules to identify Sybase Open Server 12.5 Server-Library calls in C applications

ruleset.name: ctlib
ruleset.description: Client Server Library Routines defined in cspublic.h routines

regex.name: ctpublic include
regex.description: Defines structures, types, and values used by Client-Library routines

regex.name: sybfront.h include
regex.description: sybfront.h and sybdb.h, are required in all source files that contain calls to DB-Library/C routines

regex.name: sybdb include
regex.description: sybfront.h and sybdb.h, are required in all source files that contain calls to DB-Library/C routines

ruleset.name: Client Server Library API
